            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 ring-1 ring-white/10 flex flex-col">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-poppins">Real-time Sentiment Analysis of Twitter Data</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 flex-grow">
                    Engineered a Dockerized data pipeline to stream and analyze live tweet sentiment with an LSTM model, achieving an F1-score of 0.88.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
